ine biology, international business, cybersecurity and networks, and the fine arts \xe2\x80\x93 to name just a few \xe2\x80\x93 prepare students for dynamic, in-demand careers of their choice. \n</p>\n                    <div class="btn-wrapper">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t <a class="btn" href="/admissions/apply/index.php" title="Apply">Apply</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class="btn" href="/admissions/get-info/index.php" title="Request Info">Request Info</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class="blue-bar-clear bar-container-right"></div>\n            </div><!-- /.bar-container -->\n        </section><!-- /.hero-banner -->       \n     \n     </section><!-- /#hero-region -->\t\n\t\t\n\n      <section class="snippet">\n            <div class="container">\n                <div class="col-md-6">\n                    <div class="richtext">\n                        <h2>The Best Preparation for What Comes Next</h2>\n                        <p>What makes the University of New Haven unique?  Our interdisciplinary programs and the innovative \xe2\x80\x93 and ever evolving \xe2\x80\x93 intersections we continually develop among our colleges and schools.\xc2\xa0\n</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>We pride ourselves on offering a rigorous educational experience that will challenge you in and out of the classroom. Here you will learn that curiosity is rewarded, enabling you to pursue your passion \xe2\x80\x93 or discover a new one \xe2\x80\x93 and develop the skills and experiences you need to excel in your career.\xc2\xa0 Check out our programs, and <a href="/academics/programs/">find your major. </a> </p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t                       \n                    </div><!-- /.richtext-->\n                    \n                  \n                </div>\n            </div><!-- /.container -->\n\t\t  \n\t\t  \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t <section id="hero-region" class="snippet">\n    <span class="img-filter"></span>\n \n            <section class="hero-banner hero-interior">\n            <div class="container slide-container" style="background-image: url(\'../../../_resources/images/hero/arts-on-campus.jpg\')"></div>\n            <div class="container bar-container">\n<div class="blue-bar-header" style="padding: 50px 30px 0 30px;"><div style="border-left: 3px solid #ffcc33; padding-left:20px;"><h1 style="font-size:54px;">\n\tDistinctive Consortium of Colleges and Schools</h1></div></div>\n                <div class="blue-bar bar-container-left" style="padding:30px;">\n                    <p class="blue-bar-subhead richtext" style="font-size:20px; line-height:27px;">A University of New Haven education isn\xe2\x80\x99t limited to a single major. Students take classes across the University\xe2\x80\x99s colleges and schools \xe2\x80\x93 visual artists collaborate with criminal justice students who partner with engineers. You\xe2\x80\x99ll personalize your academic journey and discover the path that\xe2\x80\x99s right for you.\n</p>\n\n\n                </div>\n                <div class="blue-bar-clear bar-container-left"></div>\n            </div><!-- /.bar-container -->\n        </section><!-- /.hero-banner -->  \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t </section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t <section class="snippet">\n            <div class="container">\n                <div class="col-md-6">\n                    <div class="richtext">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCollege of Arts and Sciences\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPick from a diverse range of majors \xe2\x80\x93 from marine biology to TV production \xe2\x80\x93 all designed to foster broad academic and interdisciplinary discovery.  \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br /><br /><a class="btn" href="/arts-sciences/" title="Learn more">Learn More</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPompea College of Business \n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThis is where you, the future entrepreneurs, executives, managers, and marketers, will gain a solid foundation in the theory, disciplines, and skills you\xe2\x80\x99ll need to climb the ladder in the corporate world \xe2\x80\x93 or to create your own business.\n<br /><br /><a class="btn" href="/business/index.php" title="Learn more">Learn More</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tHenry C. Lee College of Criminal Justice and Forensic Sciences \n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe renowned Lee College puts you firmly on a career path in national security, law enforcement, forensic or fire science, arson investigation, and many other related areas. \n<br /><br /><a class="btn" href="/lee-college/index.php" title="Learn more">Learn More</a>\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTagliatela College of Engineering \n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe Tagliatela College of Engineering is one of the leading engineering schools in the country. Known for its comprehensive, hands-on education that goes beyond the classroom, the college was established in 1920 with the founding of the University. One of the best undergraduate engineering colleges in the country, according to U.S. News & World Report 2018.\n<br /><br /><a class="btn" href="/engineering/index.php" title="Learn more">Learn More</a>\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSchool of Health Sciences \n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe School of Health Sciences delivers innovative and interdisciplinary allied health and health sciences education that draws on the distinctive identity of the University of New Haven and its partnerships with hospitals and other healthcare institutions across Connecticut and New England.\n<br /><br /><a class="btn" href="/health-sciences/" title="Learn more">Learn More</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t                       \n                       \n                    </div><!-- /.richtext-->\n                    \n                  \n                </div>\n            </div><!-- /.container -->\n\n        \n\n</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<section id="hero-region" class="snippet">\n    <span class="img-filter"></span>\n \n            <section class="hero-banner hero-interior">\n            <div class="container slide-container" style="background-image: url(\'../../../_resources/images/hero/global-learning.jpg\')"></div>\n             <div class="container bar-container">\n            \n\t\t\t\t\t'b'<div class="blue-bar-header-right" style="padding: 50px 30px 0 0;">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div style="border-right: 3px solid #ffcc33; padding-right:20px;">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h1  style="font-size:54px;">\nImmerse Yourself in Transformative Hands-On Learning Opportunities\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h1></div></div>\n                 <div class="blue-bar bar-container-right" style="padding:30px;">\n                    <p class="blue-bar-subhead richtext" style="font-size:20px; line-height:27px;">You\xe2\x80\x99ll learn just as much \xe2\x80\x93 if not more \xe2\x80\x93 through the multitude of experiences you\xe2\x80\x99ll have outside of the classroom. You\xe2\x80\x99ll work with your professors in the lab, intern in New York City, volunteer in the community, or study halfway around the globe, all while applying what you study in class.\n</p>\n\n\n                </div>\n                <div class="blue-bar-clear bar-container-right"></div>\n            </div><!-- /.bar-container -->\n        </section><!-- /.hero-banner -->  \n\t</section>\n\t\t\n\t\t <section class="snippet">\n            <div class="container">\n                <div class="col-md-6">\n                    <div class="richtext">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tStudy Abroad \n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tImmerse yourself in the culture of Italy by studying at the University of New Haven\xe2\x80\x99s satellite campus in Prato, Italy \xe2\x80\x94 located in the Tuscany region and close to Florence, the cradle of the Renaissance \xe2\x80\x94 or by participating in one of hundreds of programs that enable you to study around the globe. \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br /><br /><a class="btn" href="/academics/study-abroad/index.php" title="Learn more">Learn More</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAcademic Service-Learning\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tExamine the issues affecting our communities and participate in programs that enable you to give back and make a difference. Service learning goes beyond volunteering and teaches you how to be an engaged citizen and an agent for change. Learn more>> \n\n<br /><br /><a class="btn" href="/academics/service-learning/index.php" title="Learn more">Learn More</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tInternships\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tLong a hallmark of a University of New Haven degree program, internships enable students to learn from seasoned, well-known experts in a variety of fields, developing the sought-after skills and as well as a deep understanding of how to put what they are learning to work. The University\xe2\x80\x99s location along the New York City-Boston corridor enables students to intern at some of the most recognizable companies in the world. \n<br /><br /><a class="btn" href="/student-life/career-development-center/index.php" title="Learn more">Learn More</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFaculty-Mentored Research\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWork side-by-side with a faculty member, conducting hands-on research in the lab or in the field. You\xe2\x80\x99ll become an expert, gaining experience that will prepare you for your career or to perform intensive exploration in an advanced degree program after graduation.\n\n<br /><br /><a class="btn" href="/research/index.php" title="Learn more">Learn More</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n                       \n                       \n                    </div><!-- /.richtext-->\n                    \n                  \n                </div>\n            </div><!-- /.container -->\n\n        \n\n</section>\n           \n           \n<section id="hero-region" class="snippet">\n    <span class="img-filter"></span>\n \n            <section class="hero-banner hero-interior">\n            <div class="container slide-container" style="background-image: url(\'/_resources/images/hero/academics-experience.jpg\')"></div>\n             <div class="container bar-container">\n<div class="blue-bar-header" style="padding: 50px 30px 0 30px;"><div style="border-left: 3px solid #ffcc33; padding-left:20px;"><h1 style="font-size:54px;">\nExperience the Charger Advantage \n\n\t</h1></div></div>\n                 <div class="blue-bar bar-container-left" style="padding:30px;">\n                    <p class="blue-bar-subhead richtext" style="font-size:20px; line-height:27px;">From our thought-provoking core classes to the support you will receive from our advisers to our signature academic centers, you will quickly find that there is one singular focus at the University of New Haven: ensuring your success \xe2\x80\x93 now and for a lifetime. \n</p>\n\n\n                </div>\n                <div class="blue-bar-clear bar-container-left"></div>\n            </div><!-- /.bar-container -->\n        </section><!-- /.hero-banner -->  \n\t</section>\n       \n   \n      <section class="snippet">\n            <div class="container">\n                <div class="col-md-6">\n                    <div class="richtext">\n\n                       \n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCore Curriculum\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDesigned to complement what you learn in your major(s), the University of New Haven\xe2\x80\x99s robust core curriculum instills in you the skills employers are looking for.\n\n<br /><br /><a class="btn" href="/academics/core-curriculum.php" title="Learn more">Learn More</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAcademic Support\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe University\xe2\x80\x99s Centers for Academic Success and Advising (CASA) provide comprehensive support throughout a student\xe2\x80\x99s time at the University. From tutoring and writing support to planning your class schedule and setting academic goals, CASA helps all students realize their full potential and achieve their educational and life goals\n\n<br /><br /><a class="btn" href="/academics/academic-support/index.php" title="Learn more">Learn More</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tLibraries\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe Marvin K. Peterson Library is a central hub on the West Haven campus, offering the most advanced access to a plethora of hard-copy and electronic resources and databases that enhance the educational experience of all students.\n<br /><br /><a class="btn" href="/academics/library/index.php" title="Learn more">Learn More</a>\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tHonors Societies\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe best and brightest University of New Haven students are invited to participate in the exclusive Honors Program. Members challenge each other in and out of the class and complete an intensive thesis project. In addition, all students can earn membership in one of the many honor societies that have chapters at the University.  \n\n<br /><br /><a class="btn" href="/academics/excellence/index-old.php" title="Learn more">Learn More</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAcademic Center and Institutes\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFaculty and staff members at the University of New Haven are among the most distinguished in their fields. Many of them have created centers, initiatives, and institutes to advance their work and collaborate with other leading minds in their fields. These resources provide transformational learning opportunities for our students and provide far-reaching visibility for the world-class scholarly work that\xe2\x80\x99s taking place on campus.  \n \n\n<br /><br /><a class="btn" href="/academics/centers-institutes/index.php" title="Learn more">Learn More</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n                       \n                       \n                    </div><!-- /.richtext-->\n                    \n                  \n                </div>\n            </div><!-- /.container -->\n\n    <section id="related-links program-links" class="snippet">\n                                  <div class="container">\n  <div class="col-md-6">\n\n\t\t<div class="related">\n\t\t\t<h3 class="related-title">Resources</h3>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li><a href="/academics/course-catalog.php" title="Course Catalog" target="_blank">Course Catalog</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><a href="/academics/calendar/index.php" title="Academic Calendar">Academic Calendar and Course Schedules</a></li>\n\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><!-- /.related -->\n\t</section>\n          \n\n</section>\t\t\n\n\t\n\t\t</section>\n     \n        \n    </main><!-- /#main-content -->\n\n<footer id="site-footer" role="contentinfo">\n\n\t<span class="img-filter"></span>\n\n\t<div class="container">\n\n\t\t<!--<div id="footer-logo">\n\t\t\t<a class="white" href="/">\n\t\t\t\t<img src="/img/logo-white.svg" alt="University of New Haven logo" />\n\t\t\t\t<span class="sr-only">University of New Haven</span>\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</div>-->\n\n\t\t<div id="footer-navs">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<address>\n\t\t\t\t<a class="white" href="/"><img src="/_resources/images/centennial/cropped-centennial_logo_2c_wht_outline-2.png" style="max-width:75%;" alt="University of New Haven Centennial logo"><span c